{"tid":58574,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"腸胃炎左幾日 真係好辛苦","createTime":"2016-12-29T02:44:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T03:11:59.000Z","uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"edec069d1a8a6e5defa028c2adc6f4039b601d63","tid":58574,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T02:44:41.000Z","msg":"真係好難頂，忍唔住借朋友ac上黎嗔<br />\n<br />\n上星期貪新鮮，跟frd食左兩串豬大腸加爭先就出左事<br />\n<br />\n每日都勁頻密咁肚痛，但有無乜野痾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到琴日開始有啲野出，成身鬆晒既時候<br />\n<br />\n又到訓教便秘加肚痛，一晚醒左3，4次跟本訓得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇西醫啲藥又無用，點算好<br />\n<br />\n（利申，覺得有好轉，但仲係有啲肚痛，我懷疑係因為便秘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"7f9bee7612bed63d9d80b901124c85c2fc90882a","tid":58574,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T03:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bb1482f0ab73327a348facffabae6700b9a97a","tid":58574,"uid":19624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T03:10:49.000Z","msg":"屙清就冇事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8315605500592caf427ba1d67d6cd158a7fdb10","tid":58574,"uid":59298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T03:11:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屙清就冇事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正解<br />\n<br />\n利申 感冒未清 已經看左4次醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}